Sums of Powers of Integers
==========================

    SIGMA(k)[1..n] = 1 + 2 + ... + n = n(n+1)/2

    SIGMA(k^2)[1..n] = 1^2 + 2^2 + ... + n^2 = n(n+1)(2n+1)/6

    SIGMA(2^k)[0..m-1] = 1 + 2 + 4 ... + 2^(m-1) = 2^m - 1

    SIGMA(k*2^(k-1))[1..m] = 1x2^0 + 2x2^1 + 3x2^2 ... + m x 2^(m-1) = [(m-1) x 2^m] + 1

    IF |x| < 1
        SIGMA(x^k)[0..INF] = 1/(1-x)

        SIGMA(k*x^(k-1))[1..INF] = 1/(1-x)^2



